summary: ✨Some Advice✨
body:
✨Some Advice✨

Don’t EVER, EVER be scared to do what you want to do with your art. Don’t scared about what others think about you. Don’t be scared of the thought about “you’re not good enough” (because you are good enough! You’re style of art makes you, YOU! It’s your special individuality!!! EMBRACE IT! EXPAND ON IT!) As long as you’re not hurting somebody in the process, GO DO YOU! GET THAT SMALL IDEA IN YOUR HEAD AND SAY “FCK IT, I’M GOING TO DO IT!” Just do it for yourself, for your own fun, because if it’s just about “fitting in” or “getting popular” Then you’re not going to have fun with it. You’re just going to be constantly having anxiety about others, when in reality if you just focus on how you want to do your own art YOU’RE GOING TO HAVE A BLAST!.
